              "chord": "",
              "text": "Death cannot hold the resurrection life,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Though all its force against it may combine;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Death only gives it opportunity"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To show the boundless pow'r of life divine."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Death cannot hold the resurrection life,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The more interred, the more it multiplies;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All kinds of suff'ring only help it grow"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And fruits of life abundant realize."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Death cannot hold the resurrection life,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thru every block and barrier it breaks;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Conqu'ring the pow'r of darkness and of hell,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It swallows death and victory partakes."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Death cannot hold the resurrection life,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All of God's fulness it will manifest;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God's righteousness and holiness it yields,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His glorious image by it is expressed."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, may I know this resurrection life,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In every kind of death its pow'r outpoured,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In my experience ever realize"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This life is nought but Christ my living Lord."
            }
          ]
        }
